{"tid":1429084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李慧琼：促請特首放下身段，落區傾聽民意","createTime":"2019-08-07T12:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T13:27:34.000Z","uid":212626,"like":31,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"803004ed8204a2b4f1ca14784ef8bbdfca296ca9","tid":1429084,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:04:19.000Z","msg":"民建聯主席李慧琼表示，相信市民最想香港回復社會秩序，擔心如果香港亂下去，最後大家都要負責「埋單」。<br />\n<br />\n李慧琼指，民建聯會帶頭推動特區政府，多落區跟市民對話，亦促請特首林鄭月娥放下身段，到不同社區傾聽民意，警隊要依法執法，讓市民不用再擔心。<br />\n<br />\n對於有選民不滿民建聯議員未有到衝突現場協助街坊或了解情況，李慧琼在深圳出席港澳辦座談會後表示，如果議員走到衝突前線，會增加警員的壓力，不能夠幫到件事，強調他們是相信警方。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20190807153003\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20190807153003&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLNB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=60168ac8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20190807153003</a>"},{"pid":"3931aee8fbd63adf4da82ce591538dc14cebfe8a","tid":1429084,"uid":212626,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:08:05.000Z","msg":"連琼子都...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40d2dc54c297cd2073663ad17cdf525773d0e47","tid":1429084,"uid":156363,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:10:31.000Z","msg":"建制叫到今日即刻快閃，市民聲音一概聽唔到，佢隻耳淨係聽到中聯辦同建制把聲架咋。"},{"pid":"8f76d8ba7135f5f298c9dc6f774663bdb521aecd","tid":1429084,"uid":34877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:11:00.000Z","msg":"有無可能向動植物公園見林鄭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1428403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1428403</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5af0a816df81a772825befa7aa3a45bb3cdc33c9","tid":1429084,"uid":215876,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T